e Change Your Password</h3><p>We look forward to seeing you at the next event.</p></li><li class="news-item"><time>2011-05-02</time><h3>Mobile App Update Available on All Platforms</h3><p>Thank you for your continued patience during this transition.</p></li></ul></section><section class="module-features-grid"><h2>Funktionen</h2><div class="features-grid"><div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">◆</div><h3>Activity Log</h3><p>Control who can access what.</p></div><div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">◆</div><h3>Custom Themes</h3><p>Personalize your workspace to match your style.</p></div><div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">◆</div><h3>Real-Time Sync</h3><p>Download your data in multiple formats.</p></div><div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">◆</div><h3>Plugin System</h3><p>Find exactly what you need in seconds.</p></div><div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">◆</div><h3>API Access</h3><p>Collaborate with your entire team seamlessly.</p></div></div></section>"`;
